snippet.title: Jannie Teaches Ellie How to Swim in the Kids Pool and Plays with Fun Water Toys
snippet.description:
Jannie teaches Ellie how to swim because she doesn’t know how! Jannie has an idea to go into the kid pool to teach her and after that they have fun playing with toys in the water.
